Name: Elite Battle : Rio
About the game: Rio de Janeiro has fallen in the hands of the drug dealers. There are no distinction between the government and the crime. With almost every public institution going rogue and corrupted, a few squads and individuals still fights to reclaim the city. Join the alpha team on an elite squad and win the war! Live the experience of the BOPE squad in specific missions ! Bring back the order!
